#: index.docbook:95
#, no-c-format
msgid "Main window of &konquest;."
msgstr "Glavno okno &konquest;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:99
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&konquest; is the &kde; version of &gnu-lactic;. Players conquer other "
"planets by sending ships to them. The goal is to build an interstellar "
"empire and ultimately conqueror all other player's planets. &konquest; can "
"be played against other people or a computer."
msgstr ""
"&konquest; je &kde; različica &gnu-lactic;. Igralci osvajajo druge planete "
"tako, da nanje pošiljajo ladje. Cilj je zgraditi medzvezdni imperij in na "
"koncu osvojiti vse planete drugih igralcev. &konquest; lahko igrate proti "
"drugim osebam ali računalniku."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:108
#, no-c-format
msgid "How to Play"
msgstr "Kako igrati"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:110
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you start &konquest;, press <guibutton>New</guibutton> to start a new "
"game. You will see a dialog in which you need to enter various information "
"to setup your game. Listed below are the following parameters for the new "
"game:"
msgstr ""
"Ko zaženete &konquest;, pritisnite <guibutton>Novo</guibutton>, da začnete "
"novo igro. Videli boste pogovorno okno, v katerega morate vnesti različne "
"informacije za nastavitev igre. Spodaj so navedeni naslednji parametri za "
"novo igro:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:116
#, no-c-format
msgid "Players"
msgstr "Igralci"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:119
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Amount of players with <guibutton>Add</guibutton> or <guibutton>Remove</"
"guibutton> players"
msgstr ""
"Število igralcev z igralci <guibutton>Dodaj</guibutton> ali "
"<guibutton>Odstrani</guibutton>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:120
#, no-c-format
msgid "Names of players"
msgstr "Imena igralcev"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:121
#, no-c-format
msgid "Type of players (Computer versus Human)"
msgstr "Vrsta igralcev (računalnik proti človeku)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:122
#, no-c-format
msgid "Difficulty of computer players (Low/Normal/Hard)"
msgstr "Težavnost računalniških igralcev (nizka/normalna/težka)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:125
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To change the name of the player, double-click in the <guilabel>Name</"
"guilabel> column and edit it. To change the type of the player, open the "
"drop-down list by double-clicking in the <guilabel>Type</guilabel> column. "
"It is also possible to select the type of the new players using the drop-"
"down list of the <guibutton>Add</guibutton> button."
msgstr ""
"Če želite spremeniti ime igralca, dvokliknite v stolpec <guilabel>Ime</"
"guilabel> in ga uredite. Če želite spremeniti vrsto predvajalnika, odprite "
"spustni seznam z dvoklikom v stolpcu <guilabel>Vrsta</guilabel>. Možno je "
"tudi izbrati vrsto novih igralcev s spustnim seznamom gumba "
"<guibutton>Dodaj</guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:127
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There are two types of the human players in &konquest;, namely "
"<guimenuitem>Human (Player)</guimenuitem> and <guimenuitem>Human "
"(Spectator)</guimenuitem>. The latter option allows watching the game "
"without taking part in it."
msgstr ""
"V &konquest; obstajata dve vrsti človeških igralcev, in sicer "
"<guimenuitem>človek (igralec)</guimenuitem> in <guimenuitem>človek "
"(gledalec)</guimenuitem>. Slednja možnost omogoča ogled igre brez "
"sodelovanja v njej."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:129
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The type of AI player can be chosen from <guimenuitem>Default (Weak)</"
"guimenuitem> (a player that is neither aggressive in attacks nor in "
"defense), <guimenuitem>Default (Offensive)</guimenuitem> (an aggressive "
"attacking player) and <guimenuitem>Default (Defensive)</guimenuitem> (a "
"player with defensive strategy)."
msgstr ""
"Vrsto igralca z umetno inteligenco lahko izberete med <guimenuitem>Privzeto "
"(šibek)</guimenuitem> (igralec, ki ni niti agresiven v napadih niti v "
"obrambi), <guimenuitem>Privzeto (žaljiv)</guimenuitem> (agresiven napadalec) "
"in <guimenuitem>Privzeto (obrambno)</guimenuitem> (igralec z obrambno "
"strategijo)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:131
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Besides these classic AI players, <guimenuitem>Becai (Balanced)</"
"guimenuitem> is a balanced player taking most of <xref linkend=\"strattips\"/"
"> into account."
msgstr ""
"Poleg teh klasičnih igralcev AI je <guimenuitem>Becai (Uravnoteženi)</"
"guimenuitem> uravnotežen igralec, ki upošteva večino <xref linkend="
"\"strattips\"/>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:133
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Keep in mind that the actual difficulty of any opponent depends on your very "
"own strategy. If you play aggressively yourself, an aggressive AI player "
"might be easier to defeat than a defensive player, and vice versa."
msgstr ""
"Ne pozabite, da je dejanska težavnost katerega koli nasprotnika odvisna od "
"vaše lastne strategije. Če sami igrate agresivno, je morda lažje premagati "
"agresivnega igralca z umetno inteligenco kot obrambnega igralca in obratno."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:137
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Map</guilabel>"
msgstr "<guilabel>Zemljevid</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:138
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Neutral planets:</guilabel> Number of neutral planets."
msgstr "<guilabel>Nevtralni planeti:</guilabel> Število nevtralnih planetov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:139
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Width:</guilabel> and <guilabel>Height:</guilabel> of the map in "
"tile units."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Širina:</guilabel> in <guilabel>Višina:</guilabel> zemljevida v "
"enotah ploščic."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:140
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Changing the <guilabel>Owner:</guilabel>, <guilabel>Kill percentage:</"
"guilabel>, and <guilabel>Production:</guilabel> level of a particular planet."
msgstr ""
"Spreminjanje ravni <guilabel>Lastnik:</guilabel>, <guilabel>Odstotek "
"ubijanja:</guilabel> in <guilabel>Proizvodnja:</guilabel> določenega planeta."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:141
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Change the distribution of planets. Press <guibutton>Randomize</guibutton> "
"to make it random."
msgstr ""
"Spremenite porazdelitev planetov. Pritisnite <guibutton>Randomize</"
"guibutton>, da bo naključno."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:145
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can select the planet using the map thumbnail in the middle of "
"<guilabel>Map</guilabel> pane. Just click on the planet with the &LMB;, then "
"change the desired options."
msgstr ""
"Planet lahko izberete s sličico zemljevida na sredini podokna "
"<guilabel>Zemljevid</guilabel>. Samo kliknite na planet z &LMB;, nato "
"spremenite želene možnosti."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:149
#, no-c-format
msgid "Options"
msgstr "Možnosti"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:150
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Blind map</guilabel>: Whether or not you can see information about "
"opponents' planets."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Slepi zemljevid</guilabel>: Ali vidite informacije o "
"nasprotnikovih planetih ali ne."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:151
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Cumulative production</guilabel>: Whether or not it is enabled."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Kumulativna proizvodnja</guilabel>: ne glede na to, ali je "
"omogočeno ali ne."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:152
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Production after capture</guilabel>: If it is enabled immediately."
msgstr "<guilabel>Izdelava po zajemu</guilabel>: če je takoj omogočena."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:153
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Show ships</guilabel>: Allowing amount of ships and other stats to "
"be displayed for neutral planets."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Pokaži ladje</guilabel>: Omogoča prikaz števila ladij in drugih "
"statistik za nevtralne planete."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:154
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Show stats</guilabel>: Set the production level for neutral "
"planets."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Prikaži statistiko</guilabel>: Nastavite raven proizvodnje za "
"nevtralne planete."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:158
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you are done changing these settings (optional), click <guibutton>OK</"
"guibutton> to start the game."
msgstr ""
"Ko končate s spreminjanjem teh nastavitev (neobvezno), kliknite <guibutton>V "
"redu</guibutton>, da začnete igro."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:163
#, no-c-format
msgid "New game dialog of &konquest;"
msgstr "Novo pogovorno okno igre &konquest;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:164
#, no-c-format
msgid "New game dialog of &konquest;."
msgstr "Novo pogovorno okno igre &konquest;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:168
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Once the game starts, you will be presented the game board. Blank squares "
"are empty space. At first, each player owns one planet. The planet's "
"background is the player's color. If you move the mouse over a planet, you "
"can see additional information. Without the <guilabel>Blind map</guilabel> "
"option enabled when selecting a game, you can see any information about the "
"planet if you hover over it with mouse. If you had selected the "
"<guilabel>Blind map</guilabel> option when starting a new game, you will "
"only see the planet's name on planets which have been conquered by "
"opponents. The information can include:"
msgstr ""
"Ko se igra začne, se vam prikaže igralna plošča. Prazni kvadratki so prazen "
"prostor. Sprva ima vsak igralec en planet. Ozadje planeta je barva igralca. "
"Če premaknete miško nad planet, lahko vidite dodatne informacije. Če pri "
"izbiri igre ni omogočena možnost <guilabel>Slepi zemljevid</guilabel>, si "
"lahko ogledate vse informacije o planetu, če nad njim premaknete miško. Če "
"ste ob začetku nove igre izbrali možnost <guilabel>Slepi zemljevid</"
"guilabel>, boste videli ime planeta samo na planetih, ki so jih osvojili "
"nasprotniki. Informacije lahko vključujejo:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:173
#, no-c-format
msgid "Planet name:"
msgstr "Ime planeta:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:174
#, no-c-format
msgid "Owner:"
msgstr "Lastnik:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:175
#, no-c-format
msgid "Ships:"
msgstr "Ladje:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:176
#, no-c-format
msgid "Ships due:"
msgstr "Ladje do:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:177
#, no-c-format
msgid "Production:"
msgstr "Produkcija:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:178
#, no-c-format
msgid "Kill percent:"
msgstr "Odstotek ubijanja:"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:184
#, no-c-format
msgid "Playing &konquest;"
msgstr "Igranje &konquest;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:185
#, no-c-format
msgid "Playing &konquest;."
msgstr "Igranje &konquest;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:189
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Planet name:</guilabel> is how the planet is referred to in "
"the game. Planets are named alphabetically with uppercase letters. "
"<guilabel>Owner:</guilabel> is who owns the planet. If the planet is "
"conquered by another player, this will change. <guilabel>Ships:</guilabel> "
"is the current number of ships on the planet. <guilabel>Ships due:</"
"guilabel> will only appear if you have selected a standing order for that "
"planet, otherwise it is not there. <guilabel>Production:</guilabel> is the "
"number of ships the planet will produce each turn. The production varies "
"from planet to planet, but always remains the same. <guilabel>Kill percent:</"
"guilabel> is a measure of the effectiveness of the ships produced at that "
"planet. Attack fleets take the kill percentage of their planet of departure, "
"and defense fleets use the kill percentage of the planet they are defending. "
"You can get easily see the planet name, the owner and the current number of "
"ships on a planet in the square in which the planet lies. The owner is "
"represented by the background color of the planet, the name is in the upper "
"left corner and the number of ships is in the lower right corner."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Ime planeta:</guilabel> je planet v igri imenovan. Planeti so "
"poimenovani po abecedi z velikimi črkami. <guilabel>Lastnik:</guilabel> je "
"lastnik planeta. Če planet osvoji drug igralec, se to spremeni. "
"<guilabel>Ladje:</guilabel> je trenutno število ladij na planetu. "
"<guilabel>Zakon za pošiljanje:</guilabel> se bo prikazal le, če ste izbrali "
"trajno naročilo za ta planet, sicer ga ni. <guilabel>Proizvodnja:</guilabel> "
"je število ladij, ki jih bo planet proizvedel v vsakem obratu. Proizvodnja "
"se razlikuje od planeta do planeta, a vedno ostaja enaka. <guilabel>Odstotek "
"ubijanja:</guilabel> je merilo učinkovitosti ladij, proizvedenih na tem "
"planetu. Napadalne flote vzamejo odstotek ubijanja svojega planeta odhoda, "
"obrambne flote pa uporabljajo odstotek ubijanja planeta, ki ga branijo. Ime "
"planeta, lastnika in trenutno število ladij na planetu lahko preprosto "
"vidite v kvadratu, v katerem planet leži. Lastnik je predstavljen z barvo "
"ozadja planeta, ime je v zgornjem levem kotu in število ladij je v spodnjem "
"desnem kotu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:193
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To send ships from a planet to another, select the planet you want to send "
"ships from, enter the number of ships in the green box in the upper right "
"corner and press &Enter;. Repeat this procedure until you have sent out all "
"the ships you want. If you wish to send a constant amount of ships from one "
"planet to another every turn, enter that number and check the "
"<guilabel>Standing order</guilabel> box, and press &Enter;. The ships due to "
"the standing order will be sent at the end of the turn. When you are done, "
"press <guibutton>End Turn</guibutton>. When all players have played one "
"turn, dialog boxes will appear and give you the latest news. The game will "
"proceed like this until one of the players owns the entire galaxy."
msgstr ""
"Če želite poslati ladje z enega planeta na drugega, izberite planet, s "
"katerega želite poslati ladje, vnesite število ladij v zeleno polje v "
"zgornjem desnem kotu in pritisnite &Enter;. Ta postopek ponavljajte, dokler "
"ne razpošljete vseh želenih ladij. Če želite poslati stalno število ladij z "
"enega planeta na drugega na vsakem koraku, vnesite to številko in označite "
"polje <guilabel>Trajni nalog</guilabel> ter pritisnite &Enter;. Ladje zaradi "
"trajnega naloga bodo poslane na koncu obrata. Ko končate, pritisnite "
"<guibutton>Končaj zavoj</guibutton>. Ko vsi igralci odigrajo eno potezo, se "
"prikažejo pogovorna okna z najnovejšimi novicami. Igra bo potekala tako "
"dolgo, dokler ed od igralcev ne bo lastnik celotne galaksije."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:203
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A keyboard shortcut for <guibutton>End Turn</guibutton> action can be "
"configured using the <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Configure Shortcuts…</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item."
msgstr ""
"Bližnjico na tipkovnici za dejanje <guibutton>Končaj potezo</guibutton> "
"lahko konfigurirate z menijsko postavko <menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj bližnjice…</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:207
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For more information read the section about <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/"
"config.html#shortcuts\">Using and Customizing Shortcuts</ulink> of the &kde; "
"Fundamentals."
msgstr ""
"Za več informacij preberite razdelek o <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/"
"config.html#shortcuts\">uporabi in prilagajanju bližnjic</ulink> v &kde; "
"Osnove."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:214
#, no-c-format
msgid "Game Rules, Strategies and Tips"
msgstr "Pravila igre, strategije in nasveti"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:216
#, no-c-format
msgid "Rules"
msgstr "Pravila"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:219
#, no-c-format
msgid "Ships cannot be stopped once they leave a planet."
msgstr "Ladij ni mogoče ustaviti, ko zapustijo planet."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:220
#, no-c-format
msgid "Ships cannot attack other ships in midair."
msgstr "Ladje ne morejo napadati drugih ladij v zraku."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:221
#, no-c-format
msgid "Ships can be stored at planets for later use."
msgstr "Ladje lahko shranite na planetih za kasnejšo uporabo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:222
#, no-c-format
msgid "A planet cannot be given away."
msgstr "Planeta ni mogoče podariti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:223
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A player can skip a turn by pressing <guibutton>End Turn</guibutton> without "
"launching any ships."
msgstr ""
"Igralec lahko preskoči potezo tako, da pritisne <guibutton>Končaj potezo</"
"guibutton>, ne da bi izstrelil katero koli ladjo."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:228
#, no-c-format
msgid "Strategies and Tips"
msgstr "Strategije in nasveti"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:231
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The game is all about ship production. Try to get as many planets as "
"possible as fast as you can in order to build more ships than any of your "
"opponents."
msgstr ""
"Igra je namenjena proizvodnji ladij. Poskusite pridobiti čim več planetov, "
"kolikor je le mogoče, da bi zgradili več ladij kot kateri koli vaš "
"nasprotnik."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:232
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Do not attack a planet with less than 10 ships, unless you can conquer it."
msgstr ""
"Ne napadajte planeta z manj kot 10 ladjami, razen če ga lahko osvojite."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:233
#, no-c-format
msgid "Attack neutral planets before other players' planets."
msgstr "Napadite nevtralne planete pred planeti drugih igralcev."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:234
#, no-c-format
msgid "Split your ship storages across several planets."
msgstr "Razdelite svoja ladijska skladišča na več planetov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:235
#, no-c-format
msgid "Plan your attacks in advance."
msgstr "Napade načrtujte vnaprej."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:236
#, no-c-format
msgid "Use the ruler to find out the distance between planets."
msgstr "Z ravnilom ugotovite razdaljo med planeti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:237
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use the information window to get information on planets before an attack."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite informacijsko okno za pridobitev informacij o planetih pred "
"napadom."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:238
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If this information is available to you, it is preferable to attack a planet "
"with a low kill ratio from a planet with a high one."
msgstr ""
"Če so vam te informacije na voljo, je bolje, da napadete planet z nizkim "
"številom ubijanj s planeta z visokim."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:244
#, no-c-format
msgid "Menus"
msgstr "Meniji"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:247
#, no-c-format
msgid "Menu Items"
msgstr "Elementi menija"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:251
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>N</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Game</guimenu> <guimenuitem>New</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>N</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Igra</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Nova</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:258
#, no-c-format
msgid "Starts a new game."
msgstr "Začne novo igro."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:262
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&End;</keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Game</guimenu> <guimenuitem>End Game</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&End;</keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Igra</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Končaj igro</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:269
#, no-c-format
msgid "<action>End the current game, without closing</action> &konquest;."
msgstr "<action>Končajte trenutno igro, ne da bi zaprli</action> &konquest;."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:273
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Game</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Measure Distance…</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Igra</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Izmeri razdaljo…</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:277
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Allows to measure the distance.</action> Click with the &LMB; on two "
"planets to see their distance."
msgstr ""
"<action>Omogoča merjenje razdalje.</action> Kliknite z &LMB; na dveh "
"planetih, da vidite njuno oddaljenost."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:281
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Game</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Fleet Overview</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Igra</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Pregled flote…</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:285
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Opens a window</action> to display detailed information for all "
"fleets."
msgstr ""
"<action>Odpre okno</action> za prikaz podrobnih informacij za vse flote."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:290
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Game</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Quit</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Igra</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Zapusti</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:297
#, no-c-format
msgid "Quits the game."
msgstr "Zapusti igro."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:301
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Move</guimenu> <guimenuitem>End Turn</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Premik</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Končaj potezo</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:305
#, no-c-format
msgid "Allows you to <action>end turn</action> from the main menu."
msgstr "Omogoča vam, da <action>končate potezo</action> iz glavnega menija."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:309
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Show Messages</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Prikaži sporočila</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:313
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show or hide the messages panel."
msgstr "Prikaži ali skrij ploščo s sporočili."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:317
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Show Standings</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Ogled</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Prikaži stanja</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:321
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show or hide the current player standings table."
msgstr "Pokaži ali skrij trenutno tabelo stanj igralca."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:326
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Additionally &konquest; has the common &kde; <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> and "
"<guimenu>Help</guimenu> menu items, for more information read the sections "
"about the <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html#menus-settings"
"\">Settings Menu</ulink> and <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus."
"html#menus-help\">Help Menu</ulink> of the &kde; Fundamentals."
msgstr ""
"Poleg tega &konquest; ima skupno &kde; Elemente menija <guimenu>Nastavitve</"
"guimenu> in <guimenu>Pomoč</guimenu>, za več informacij preberite razdelke o "
"<ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html#menus-settings\">meniju z "
"nastavitvami</ulink> in <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html#menus-help"
"\">meni Pomoč</ulink> v &kde; Osnove."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:336
#, no-c-format
msgid "Frequently Asked Questions"
msgstr "Pogosto zastavljena vprašanja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:340
#, no-c-format
msgid "Can I redirect ships once they have left a planet?"
msgstr "Ali lahko preusmerim ladje, ko zapustijo planet?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:341
#, no-c-format
msgid "No, once ships leave a planet, they cannot be stopped or redirected."
msgstr ""
"Ne, ko ladje enkrat zapustijo planet, jih ni več mogoče ustaviti ali "
"preusmeriti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:345
#, no-c-format
msgid "Do the different colors and shapes of planets mean anything?"
msgstr "Ali različne barve in oblike planetov kaj pomenijo?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:346
#, no-c-format
msgid "No, they are random."
msgstr "Ne, naključne so."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:350
#, no-c-format
msgid "How can I know where my ships are?"
msgstr "Kako lahko vem, kje so moje ladje?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:351
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click <guibutton>Show Standings</guibutton>. It will give you information "
"about fleets currently in flight."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite <guibutton>Prikaži stanja</guibutton>. Dal vam bo informacije o "
"flotah, ki trenutno letijo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:355
#, no-c-format
msgid "I have lost all my planets, but I am still in the game, why?"
msgstr "Izgubil sem vse svoje planete, vendar sem še vedno v igri, zakaj?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:356
#, no-c-format
msgid "You have not lost the game until you have lost all your ships."
msgstr "Igre niste izgubili, dokler ne izgubite vseh svojih ladij."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:360
#, no-c-format
msgid "Can I store ships on a planet for later use?"
msgstr "Ali lahko shranim ladje na planet za kasnejšo uporabo?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:361
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Yes, you should however store them on multiple planets to be able to send "
"them to nearby planets."
msgstr ""
"Da, vendar bi jih morali shraniti na več planetih, da bi jih lahko poslali "
"na bližnje planete."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:365
#, no-c-format
msgid "Is it possible to change the theme?"
msgstr "Ali je možno spremeniti temo?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:366
#, no-c-format
msgid "No, that is not possible at the moment."
msgstr "Ne, to trenutno ni mogoče."

